  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    MORDefinitionObjectProperty, MORDomainObjectProperty, MORFullObjectProperty, MORHierarchicalObjectProperty

    public abstract class MORObjectPropertyBase
extends MORBase<org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLObjectProperty>
implements MORObjectProperty
    The base MORObjectProperty class Descriptor.

    This class is shared between all the Descriptors that uses aMOR. It is just define MORBase for an ObjectInstance to be used for MORObjectPropertys. Please, see those classes for more documentations.
